1 About

Additional analyses for the manuscript:

  • Fine-mapping on all SNPs, including those outside the long ancestry segments;
  • Phenotype modeling and association analysis on a subset of individuals: consider current smokers and exclude current non-smokers

Links

  • Supplementaty figures v1: https://hemostat.github.io/Public/Papers/06-int-acs-copdgene/supp-figures.html
